  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a copper mug over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for an additional minute.",
    "Add the ground lamb and cook until it is browned, breaking it up into small pieces as it cooks.",
    "Add the ground annatto, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Add the tomato paste and stir to combine.",
    "Add the water and bring the mixture to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer, covered, for 20 minutes.",
    "Serve the stew hot, garnished with chopped fresh herbs if desired."
  ],
